        "subject": "LU-4017 pools: generate pool ID for OST pools",
        "message": "LU-4017 pools: generate pool ID for OST pools\n\nThis patch try to add a unique pool id for every pool, pool id\nis unique identifier for every pool.\n\nPool id is added for project quota, we use ost pool to manage\ninode project quota, project quota design need an id for every\ninode, and quota usages are grouped by this id. after OST pool\nid is added, we can enforce project quota by using existed ost\npool attributes to file.\n\nPool ID is saved in MGS llog too, for old system which contains\nsome OST pools saved in MGS llog, it will return -EINVAL.\nAdministrators need destroy old ost pool and regenerate them\nwith new format.\n\nAslo add quota aware support when creating\nand destroying OST pool.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nSigned-off-by: Wang Shilong <wshilong@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I0225d1d09e08cccafaeecb481f0cb39d83ada267\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
